# Contact form email delivery (Web3Forms — https://web3forms.com)
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com, enter your Gmail, and they email you an Access Key.
# 2. Add this in Vercel: Project → Settings → Environment Variables, then REDEPLOY.
#
# NOTE: this is a NEXT_PUBLIC_ variable — the form submits to Web3Forms directly
# from the browser (Web3Forms' intended usage; server-side calls get blocked by
# Cloudflare). Web3Forms access keys are public by design, so this is expected.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=
